{"tid":1689144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有醫生指證有黑警強姦及性侵女示威者","createTime":"2019-11-02T16:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T16:55:21.000Z","uid":233692,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6b3e8cc2b394d470a83d6462971847a8b102d5f9","tid":1689144,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:50:52.000Z","msg":"第一二項唔係傳言，恕不詳述。<br />\n<br />\n若果我有半句虛言，天人共鑑。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n（9:30）<br />\n<br />\n其實我本來想呻兩句嘅啫，點知變到好似引爆核彈咁。<br />\n<br />\n我無野講，都唔會自殺。<br />\n<br />\n當街當巷都蒙面無冧巴啦，要受害者出來，再舉證入罪，其實真係難上加難。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VVeqcjz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVVeqcjz.png&h=1fd57b7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f9402d68246c0c3c835125459af779456c562b0","tid":1689144,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:52:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62ecbfbdd4efdb084426e924e0edcb38720cc76d","tid":1689144,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:52:57.000Z","msg":"重點頭兩項再唔係謠言"},{"pid":"5441791715948dd47241bf541e92fb6ea8ade657","tid":1689144,"uid":99351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:54:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0746872fde7d9efb50cc2c8cdcaa4b7db3971b40","tid":1689144,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:54:15.000Z","msg":"淨係好嬲好嬲無用架"},{"pid":"508d05d089114ffa7dfa82c81f85746acec06700","tid":1689144,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:55:21.000Z","msg":"推"}]}